Sec. 3. 9 V.S.A. § 2466d is added to read:
§ 2466d. REPORTING OF MEDICAL DEBT INFORMATION
PROHIBITED
(a) A credit reporting agency shall not report or maintain in the file on a
consumer information relating to a medical debt.
(b) As used in this section:

